1
00:00:00,076 --> 00:00:05,076
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,000
Lin Juan has already taken
down the ninth challenger.

3
00:00:06,220 --> 00:00:08,080
Does anyone else want to challenge?

4
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:09,920
Congratulations.

5
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:15,120
Here is your prize.

6
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:19,210
I thought the prize was the fragment.

7
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:20,620
That one?

8
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:22,790
That prize costs you your life.

9
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:32,040
Are we really using the
same way to get in again?

10
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:34,750
Unless you want to get ambushed again.

11
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,420
So what is our next step?

12
00:00:50,290 --> 00:00:51,410
It's been an exhausting day.

13
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:53,420
Let's dodge everything
for one night and relax.

14
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:16,050
I'll scratch your back
to help you loosen up.

15
00:01:20,790 --> 00:01:22,040
You really don't have to.

16
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,306
A little scratch before bed.

17
00:01:24,330 --> 00:01:25,516
It's relaxing and good for you.

18
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:26,540
Never heard of that?

19
00:01:28,670 --> 00:01:29,670
Is this okay?

20
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,920
A little to the left.

21
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:34,250
Left.

22
00:01:37,670 --> 00:01:38,750
How does the pressure feel?

23
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:42,726
A bit more to the left.

24
00:01:42,750 --> 00:01:43,750
More to the left.

25
00:01:44,290 --> 00:01:45,290
Right there.

26
00:02:28,790 --> 00:02:30,580
The owner of that boxing gym is Lu Ziye.

27
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,096
After pulling an all-nighter,
he comes here every day

28
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,210
for a bowl of hot soup.

29
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,160
We'll wait and catch him then.

30
00:02:35,290 --> 00:02:36,290
Talk to him first.

31
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:50,580
Don't drink it.

32
00:02:51,210 --> 00:02:52,210
The water tastes strange.

33
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:03,910
This place isn't the real deal.

34
00:03:04,290 --> 00:03:05,290
Let's go somewhere else.

35
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,180
[WANTED BEAD OR AIVE]

36
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:24,170
Looks like they're coming after me.

37
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,170
We should split up for now.

38
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:31,710
Have Lin Juan stay and cover you.

39
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,820
I'll make sure you get back safely.

40
00:03:39,290 --> 00:03:40,290
Be careful.

41
00:03:42,210 --> 00:03:43,830
Don't go too hard on them.

42
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:47,920
Go.

43
00:03:58,710 --> 00:03:59,710
Come out.

44
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:03,000
Take me to your boss.

45
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,080
Nongyu, over here.

46
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,710
Why are you here?

47
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:12,870
Mr. Wu sent me.

48
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,096
His watch picked up signs that.

49
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,686
Nongyu might be in danger around this area.

50
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,756
I was nearby at the time.

51
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:17,860
So he sent me over to help.

52
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:22,670
Go help Xie Xinxu first.

53
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,080
Mr. Gu.

54
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:26,930
If you do not form a pact with me today,

55
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,230
I will go out and tell everyone

56
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:30,570
that you are a Ren.

57
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:32,420
Hahahaha.

58
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:38,540
Why are you here?

59
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:42,040
The owner of that boxing
gym your friend went to

60
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,250
is my husband.

61
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:48,170
Welcome to

62
00:05:48,590 --> 00:05:49,660
my Mugang.

63
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,080
Your Mugang?

64
00:05:57,420 --> 00:05:58,420
I forgot to tell you.

65
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:01,440
My mother is the head of the
Special Administration Bureau.

66
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,420
Most of this place is her business.

67
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:09,420
I just help her

68
00:06:09,670 --> 00:06:10,670
manage it for now.

69
00:06:12,210 --> 00:06:13,057
So,

70
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:16,186
So you put out a warrant for me because
I crossed into your illicit operations?

71
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:18,010
Of course it was because
I wanted to see you.

72
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:19,476
My people

73
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,500
said they spotted you,

74
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,960
so I issued the warrant
right away to find you.

75
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:25,210
How do you think your husband would feel

76
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,230
if he heard that?

77
00:06:27,690 --> 00:06:28,690
Is it appropriate?

78
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:31,646
That useless husband of mine

79
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:33,110
is nothing more than a blood supply.

80
00:06:33,290 --> 00:06:34,540
You are the only one I like.

81
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:35,670
Sorry.

82
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,540
I have no interest in you at all.

83
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:44,790
I was going to keep you
here a couple more days.

84
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:47,170
But my mother was right.

85
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,620
Men

86
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,080
are all the same.

87
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,830
Building a career is what really matters.

88
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,170
The news about the third fragment was fake.

89
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:01,080
My mother only used it as bait

90
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,646
to take you,

91
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:03,696
Wu Siyuan,

92
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,080
and everyone connected to you out.

93
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:07,500
Lin Juan managed to dodge it last time.

94
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,920
That one?

95
00:07:09,170 --> 00:07:10,850
That was meant to be traded for your life.

96
00:07:11,590 --> 00:07:12,590
But this time,

97
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:14,420
we are fully prepared.

98
00:07:21,670 --> 00:07:22,670
I suppose.

99
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:24,580
Secretary Zhang

100
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,580
has already picked up Wu Nongyu.

101
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,470
[Lu Ziye]

102
00:08:06,140 --> 00:08:07,760
What do you mean by useless husband?

103
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:11,660
You planted people
around me again, didn't you?

104
00:08:12,790 --> 00:08:15,000
You must look awful right now.

105
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,650
If you're too ugly,

106
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,226
I won't even bother

107
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:19,870
letting you live off me.

108
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:37,890
[Xu]

109
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,120
Nongyu, I'm sorry.

110
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:55,660
But I can't let you and
Mr. Wu bring down the Bureau.

111
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,160
What are you going to do to me?

112
00:08:57,290 --> 00:08:59,210
This area of Mugang has
a complex mix of people.

113
00:08:59,290 --> 00:09:01,136
There have been cases of escaped Ren

114
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,640
banding together to commit robberies.

115
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:05,960
If you die at their hands,

116
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:07,660
it would be good for all of us.

117
00:09:27,830 --> 00:09:28,830
Back off.

118
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:39,830
Nobody move.

119
00:09:40,470 --> 00:09:41,500
Hands up.

120
00:09:42,170 --> 00:09:43,170
Everyone stay still.

121
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,600
Keep making noise and I'll shoot you.

122
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:50,820
Get down.

123
00:09:50,850 --> 00:09:51,850
Come out on your own.

124
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:53,620
Come out.

125
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:56,396
Out of the car.

126
00:09:56,420 --> 00:09:56,976
Now.

127
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:57,686
Turn around yourself.

128
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:58,080
Hands.

129
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,620
Move.

130
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:01,140
Don't move.

131
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,670
Behave.

132
00:10:05,170 --> 00:10:07,230
Take the latest inhibitor
and the Yin with you.

133
00:10:07,610 --> 00:10:08,610
Yes.

134
00:10:18,690 --> 00:10:19,970
Nobody move.

135
00:10:22,190 --> 00:10:23,190
Behave.

136
00:10:24,290 --> 00:10:25,460
Untie her hands.

137
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:42,266
Hello, Wei.

138
00:10:42,290 --> 00:10:43,000
Calling Ye.

139
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,810
[Calling Ye…]

140
00:10:45,830 --> 00:10:46,620
So noisy.

141
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,767
We just got robbed.

142
00:10:47,791 --> 00:10:49,396
And the Yin we brought was taken.

143
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:50,267
Go find them.

144
00:10:50,291 --> 00:10:51,556
On my turf,

145
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:53,870
no one takes anything from me.

146
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,370
Stop it.

147
00:11:04,710 --> 00:11:05,460
Go sit and wait.

148
00:11:05,710 --> 00:11:06,710
It will be over soon.

149
00:11:06,830 --> 00:11:07,830
No.

150
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,320
It's my birthday today.

151
00:11:18,540 --> 00:11:19,990
And this dinner is all you prepared?

152
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,520
No gift?

153
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:22,810
There is.

154
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,330
In this pocket.

155
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,000
There's no other gift.

156
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,700
It's just the watch vibrating.

157
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:38,010
I wanted you to take it out and check.

158
00:11:40,770 --> 00:11:43,220
[SOS Wu Nongyu]

159
00:11:43,850 --> 00:11:45,010
Nongyu seems to be in danger.

160
00:11:47,310 --> 00:11:48,890
[SOS Wu Nongyu]

161
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:52,110
She's not here.

162
00:11:58,310 --> 00:11:59,520
[Wu]

163
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:03,620
Are you with Nongyu right now?

164
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,250
Secretary Zhang lured her away.

165
00:12:05,570 --> 00:12:06,057
Most likely,

166
00:12:06,081 --> 00:12:08,401
she acted under Xia Shang's
orders and is going after her.

167
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:09,960
Her watch sent me a location.

168
00:12:10,370 --> 00:12:11,370
Find her first.

169
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,710
What exactly was going
on with that group just now?

170
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,370
I've already notified Siyuan.

171
00:12:47,710 --> 00:12:49,250
Let's find a place to hide for now.

172
00:13:02,060 --> 00:13:05,520
[Emergency contact is 83 km away]

173
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,110
So this is where you were hiding.

174
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,710
The scent of Yin.

175
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,580
Judging by the silhouette,
looks like a handsome guy.

176
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,670
I can't hold back anymore, girls.

177
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:33,900
Out of bullets.

178
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,900
Perfect.

179
00:14:59,950 --> 00:15:01,750
So the two of you came together to die?

180
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:05,170
No.

181
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,900
Don't get in the way.

182
00:15:41,330 --> 00:15:42,460
Not bad, that manhole cover.

183
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:46,470
That's just a lousy medal from
that underground boxing match.

184
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:49,447
Well then,

185
00:15:49,471 --> 00:15:51,790
my baby has a fun new toy.

186
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:55,370
Lin Juan.

187
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:11,390
♪ You smell like something strange ♪

188
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:13,406
♪ Like wood ♪

189
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:14,197
♪ Like wine ♪

190
00:16:14,221 --> 00:16:16,350
♪ Like the fading rain ♪

191
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:20,286
♪ It's not a problem I can fix ♪

192
00:16:20,310 --> 00:16:23,680
♪ Maybe I'm just meant to be your toy… ♪

193
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,347
Brothers.

194
00:16:28,371 --> 00:16:29,376
Bring out your babies.

195
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,460
Don't let them get away!

196
00:16:38,210 --> 00:16:39,210
Let's split it.

197
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:40,260
Half and half.

198
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:41,520
You can have it all.

199
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:56,780
Right on time.

200
00:17:34,810 --> 00:17:40,100
♪ The touch of your warm embrace ♪

201
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:42,616
♪ I'm a slave to you ♪

202
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:45,140
♪ Can you feel that you're my fire? ♪

203
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:56,350
♪ Listening to your whispers,
wrapped in your dangerous presence ♪

204
00:17:56,770 --> 00:17:59,770
♪ The touch of your warm embrace ♪

205
00:18:00,470 --> 00:18:02,196
♪ I'm a slave to you ♪

206
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:06,970
♪ Can you feel that you're my fire? ♪

207
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:21,350
♪ You smell like something strange ♪

208
00:18:22,810 --> 00:18:23,366
♪ Like wood ♪

209
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:24,157
♪ Like wine ♪

210
00:18:24,181 --> 00:18:26,310
♪ Like the fading rain ♪

211
00:18:26,810 --> 00:18:30,246
♪ It's not a problem I can fix ♪

212
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:33,640
♪ Maybe I'm just meant to be your toy ♪
